comments: Jokic (DEN) brings his hands towards Niang (PHI) and marginal contact occurs as he releases from the contact.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Jokic (DEN) is the last player to touch the ball before the ball goes out of bounds.  Possession is correctly awarded to Philadelphia.
Barton (DEN) moves slightly forward towards Harden (PHI) and marginal contact occurs as Harden passes the ball.
Niang (PHI) and Green (DEN) come together at the same spot and marginal contact occurs as Embiid (PHI) secures the rebound.
Jokic (DEN) absorbs the contact from Maxey (PHI) and avoids making contact with Maxey's arm as he defends the driving shot attempt.
Maxey (PHI) commits a take foul on Jokic (DEN).
Thybulle (PHI) commits a take foul on Barton (DEN).
Embiid (PHI) is already in Rivers' (DEN) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Green (DEN) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he begins to imminently exit the lane.
Green (DEN) legally contests Niang's (PHI) jump shot attempt.

Niang (PHI) moves forward into Jokic's (DEN) body and initiates contact that causes Jokic to step out of bounds.  After communicating with the Replay Center, it was determined the foul occurred prior to the expiration of the game clock, and the game clock was reset to 01.2.
